{"tid":2139561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗疫大漏洞】獲豁免檢疫中港貨車四圍走 除口罩開工隨時大疫爆","createTime":"2020-08-04T11:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T06:12:01.000Z","uid":259088,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"16fa888becb57ae5bc5e9c5e4ada7b35379f2158","tid":2139561,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jGzVj3c2tVrgdPDJoGsE4kbN-Og=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4IASCN3UGMK55OPFFK3FFIA6GM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjGzVj3c2tVrgdPDJoGsE4kbN-Og%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4IASCN3UGMK55OPFFK3FFIA6GM.jpg&h=a68e2c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情尚未受控，每日均有過百確診。早前食衞局長陳肇始承認，豁免檢疫致第三波疫情大爆發；而<strong><span class=\"x-large\">在豁免檢疫的名單中有至少四萬人，跨境貨車司機就佔至少一萬人</span></strong>，而在7月27日，亦有首名中港司機確診。<strong>政府現時未對貨場等眾多免檢疫人士出入的地方，要求加強防疫如為進入貨場者量體溫等，僅呼籲司機戴口罩及加強個人衞生</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n但《蘋果》上月底就到落馬洲、新田一帶，跟隨中港貨櫃車行蹤，就發現有<strong><span class=\"x-large\">三大防疫漏洞</span></strong>，<strong><span class=\"red\">包括有中港貨車司機在車上無戴口罩，駛到屋苑與街坊交收貨品、中港司機「自出自入」大型貨場，而貨場並無為外來者量體溫或消毒，及酷熱天氣下，貨場亦有不少工人除罩開工、與中港司機共用食堂。</span></strong>有醫生警告，貨場欠缺防疫措施，若有確診者到訪，隨時引發成「貨場群組」。<br />\n<br />\n根據政府的最新數字，6月至7月22日，衞生署合共發出85,527份獲豁免人士醫學監察通知書。<strong>政府上月中曾指，豁免入境檢疫導致大爆發的說法是「誤解」；至月底有專家以病毒基因作分析，陳肇始才改口稱病毒基因屬「實證」，會嚴肅跟進。</strong>《蘋果》於7月24日及28日，到落馬洲附近、較多中港貨櫃車司機聚腳的新田一帶，隨機抽取兩架中港貨櫃車，了解中港貨櫃車去向。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>漏洞1：自出自入貨場 無量體溫</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-X_LZbfpdh9W7b4QuXWQd1plmqo=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7COUA2JZRYCENCNR6WL57DS3QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-X_LZbfpdh9W7b4QuXWQd1plmqo%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7COUA2JZRYCENCNR6WL57DS3QY.jpg&h=6d0ce154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有知情者向《蘋果》指，嘉民領達中心地下私家車停車場同時供貨車停泊，入閘處沒有量度體溫的設備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A7MU89k-zM3jzlv80r04s3YvfQY=/640x311/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJSBIVCVQIMB6FYOMEB2DSB53E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA7MU89k-zM3jzlv80r04s3YvfQY%3D%2F640x311%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJSBIVCVQIMB6FYOMEB2DSB53E.jpg&h=7c2c6e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有每日出入嘉民領達中心的貨車司機向《蘋果》指，中心曾有懷疑確診個案時，貨車入閘處有職員為入場司機量體溫，「但之後已經無做」。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>漏洞2：駕車無戴罩 與街坊交收</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DX4qUyMlHvLgwzZ9yFJOqKfVJg8=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LX7FUJGTWFSYYHCWFTOPGBTG2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDX4qUyMlHvLgwzZ9yFJOqKfVJg8%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLX7FUJGTWFSYYHCWFTOPGBTG2Y.jpg&h=6da685fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在鄰近落馬洲的新田一帶，不難見到有中港貨車司機除罩駕車。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fEW8p7pJG5Pxx9CSlGvAzosuTis=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C3VZJ6BBB3XLYWMXEYGMFJYWIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfEW8p7pJG5Pxx9CSlGvAzosuTis%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC3VZJ6BBB3XLYWMXEYGMFJYWIA.jpg&h=ab66d8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司機離開貨櫃場飯堂駕車離開時，在車內並無戴上口罩，其後到天水圍與街坊交收。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2GwMnEgykiUPjPZ88kRSEDKNitY=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OJKOMJXHFBFTNCVJGPFZK6EAUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2GwMnEgykiUPjPZ88kRSEDKNitY%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOJKOMJXHFBFTNCVJGPFZK6EAUQ.jpg&h=c90d9dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n街坊從中港司機手上取走兩袋物品。（黃色及藍色膠袋）<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>漏洞3：與機場貨場工人共用食堂</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RT15GJ29_SjBbwEied6IBLlLpEk=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VCE2OLHV7J32Q7E5OG4HAYEKHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRT15GJ29_SjBbwEied6IBLlLpEk%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVCE2OLHV7J32Q7E5OG4HAYEKHM.jpg&h=b23f66b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有中港司機進入機場空運中心停車場時，並無戴上口罩，入閘處亦無人為司機量度體溫。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Krmv4eVvUBsgqL0_mbdl0hw2fp8=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XEVDOH5Z3SQMAGBDE4XMG32FII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKrmv4eVvUBsgqL0_mbdl0hw2fp8%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXEVDOH5Z3SQMAGBDE4XMG32FII.jpg&h=82d80186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機場空運中心貨場內，亦有工人除罩工作。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄 蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/UZK7BVBEVK3BH6XGDHXZJOIYXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2FUZK7BVBEVK3BH6XGDHXZJOIYXA%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=d168f385\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2FUZK7BVBEVK3BH6XGDHXZJOIYXA%2F&h=06443745\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/UZK7BVBEVK3BH6XGDHXZJOIYXA/</a>"},{"pid":"4b2795699e5ab5f7a2c6a5dd25347ee18e9021b0","tid":2139561,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cbea67c42abe1c0054dc312085531d99b2d187","tid":2139561,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8355e410c52e997b935cfc2102a745df1c49babb","tid":2139561,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0b7bf372626ae48183276eb2c949dd5c66544d","tid":2139561,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdcecd42fca4d5ffd05716e6a662e6f75238042","tid":2139561,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit